{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/face-masks/what-purpose-face-masks","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"What is the purpose of face masks?","meta_description":"Face masks are one of the most effective measures that help reduce spreading of the virus.","content":{"processed":"<h2><strong>Recommendations</strong></h2>\n<p>Face masks (or other face coverings that cover your mouth and nose) are one of the <strong>most effective measures </strong>that help reduce spreading of the virus. The face covering helps to avoid spreading of the virus by stopping the respiratory droplets which contain viral particles.</p>\n<p>Face masks are only effective when <strong>worn correctly</strong> – over your nose and your mouth – and <a href=\"https://aatishb.com/maskmath/index-cs.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\"><strong>handled correctly</strong>.</a></p>\n<p>Face masks are used to prevent spreading of COVID -19 and are recommended by sufficient professional organizers including the World Health Organization (WHO). To cover your mouth and nose, it is recommended to use <strong>face masks </strong>(either medical or textile masks), <strong>respirators </strong>or <strong>scarves</strong>. </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks/what-purpose-face-masks"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-05T11:58:11+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://koronavirus.mzcr.cz/co-je-rouska-a-jak-ma-vypadat/","title":"Detailed information about the effectiveness of wearing face masks can be found for example here"}],"relationships":{"region":[],"icon":null,"situation_type":{"name":"Face masks","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"masks"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Types of protection","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks/types-protection","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"How to take care of the face mask","path":{"alias